data.description: Enjoy the charm of this home situated in the heart of historic Port Norfolk. A Quaint 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence in an excellent setting. A spacious main-level bedroom adjacent to a full bath, while the second floor boasts 4 sizable bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and jetted tub. Generous living and dining spaces, along with an eat-in kitchen. Large detached garage with ample storage, complete with a large fenced backyard for gardening and enjoying the outdoors. New downstairs  HVAC system(2021).
